{"tid":1209578,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"下一次應該點升級","createTime":"2019-06-12T11:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T11:54:18.000Z","uid":9813,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7da5d1c547238898209cac5f72272fc4e966bebd","tid":1209578,"uid":9813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:48:17.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"4162ee7e17ea40e8664bf648527e55e57ea186aa","tid":1209578,"uid":88263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:54:18.000Z","msg":"石禮謙話畀大家知，香港人最緊張嘅係經濟<br />\n<br />\n講個知識畀大家知<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">每塞6分鐘車，就會有28億損失</span></span><br />\n<br />\n舊Source： <a href=\"https://www.master-insight.com/塞車造成多少經濟損失？/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.master-insight.com%2F%E5%A1%9E%E8%BB%8A%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1%EF%BC%9F%2F&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIgVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=4f210237\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.master-insight.com/塞車造成多少經濟損失？/</a><br />\n<br />\n重鐵同時間載到40幾萬人，繁忙時間以每平方米4個人計嘅運載量到9成<br />\n<br />\n只要帶手提行李就會每平方米大約企到2個人，即係20幾萬人會打爆重鐵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">舉個例子</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">100萬人遊行散場，要現有運載力嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5倍</span>先可以運走啲人</span></span>，但留意返香港有7百幾萬人，又有遊客。一百萬人散場，實際所需運載力係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大過5倍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家請守法體驗一流港鐵服務<br />\n[香港命脈][野餐以外]一星期暢遊港鐵體驗包 [鐵膠推介]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1205357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1205357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}